               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17561020-24-off112-c143" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-defend189 t17561020-24-off112 t17561020-24-verdict115"></join>
         
               <p>422. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17561020-24-defend189" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Molloy 
                  <interp inst="t17561020-24-defend189" type="surname" value="Molloy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-defend189" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-defend189" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17561020-24-deflabel111" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-defend189 t17561020-24-deflabel111"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17561020-24-off112" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-off112" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-off112" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing four yards of silk, value 15 s
            </rs>. the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17561020-24-victim191" type="victimName">
                     Christopher 
                     Lorain 
                  <interp inst="t17561020-24-victim191" type="surname" value="Lorain"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-victim191" type="given" value="Christopher"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-victim191" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-off112 t17561020-24-victim191"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17561020-24-cd113" type="crimeDate">Oct. 2</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-off112 t17561020-24-cd113"></join>.* </p> 
               <p>Christopher Lorain. I am a <rs id="t17561020-24-viclabel114" type="occupation">taylor</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-victim191 t17561020-24-viclabel114"></join>, and live at the back of St. Clement's. The prisoner came into my shop on the 2d of October, and took two pieces of silk. I went out, and took her with them upon her (produced in court, and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Q. Did you know the prisoner before?</p>
               <p>Lorain. No. I never saw her before that time to my knowledge.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you see her in the shop?</p>
               <p>Lorain. No, I did not. My little girl call'd, and said, papa, a woman has carried two rolls of silk out of the shop; so I ran out.</p>
               <p>Q. What time of the day was this?</p>
               <p>Lorain. Between nine and ten in the morning. She own'd she took them, and beg'd for mercy; saying. she did it through necessity, wanting money to carry her down into Kent to her friends.</p>
               <p>Q. What is the value of the silk?</p>
               <p>Lorain. It is worth fourteen shillings.</p>
               <p>The prisoner had nothing to say in her defence.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17561020-24-verdict115" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-verdict115" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-verdict115" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               Guilty 14 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17561020-24-punish116" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17561020-24-punish116" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17561020-24-defend189 t17561020-24-punish116"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
